    <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-weight: bold;">ç”Ÿæˆçš„ä»£ç ï¼ˆç›´æ¥å¤åˆ¶åˆ° allLessons é‡Œï¼‰ï¼š</p>
    <textarea id="finalOutput" style="width: 100%; height: 150px; padding: 10px; background: #fafafa; border: 1px solid #ccc;" readonly></textarea>
